Estimated student:

At the moment you complete the registration through the UMOVE application, you will receive the credentials of the UJA ICT Account:

User: ${user}

Password: ${password}

In addition, with the same credentials, you can access the email of Uja students (@red.ujaen.es) where you will receive all the information and notices. Therefore, it is very important to activate this GMAIL account and read the post office that you receive.

You can enter the UJA email through:

Intranet: <https://www.ujaen.es/intranet>  
GMAIL Mail Option. Using the Username: ${user} and Password: ${password}

Via GOOGLE, UJA email is a GMAIL (GOOGLE) account. Using the following user: ${user}@red.ujaen.es, and the same password from the previous section: ${password}
